,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"295dbb7a8c23c0beaf205a96cdd7a7e3d9918d73","tid":1984344,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:44:10.000Z","msg":"唔好覺得大家都唔會信李桂華講野，條友係正名緊新疆化同加強青年人=恐怖分子既刻版印象。我地點諗都改變唔到佢繼續作故仔。<br />\n想靠老妨上總警司？我屌你老母喇，O記=全港最大毒品集團<br />\n趁依家推23條搵打靶仔轉移視線，順手煲埋佢喇。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"個個獨裁者都會抹黑反對派為暴徒<br />\n六四成班學生都俾人話暴徒<br />\n我地繼續抵抗<br />\n屌9返佢係恐怖份子<br />\n輿論同意識形態唔可以輸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3310aad6a535b91f87739edd4d91cd8c4957c7b7","tid":1984344,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"其實好多有少少錢籃屍心裏重驚過黃絲，密密開始搬嘢走，港紙好快玩卵完"},{"pid":"67eff020c1d9304eacb732c46f0213579dbe270d","tid":1984344,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"登記做選民！"},{"pid":"dcc85017e6f782980d218b354bd6a7aa78bfb85b","tid":1984344,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:07:36.000Z","msg":"支持手足"},{"pid":"9ee0b02be5f08d856c4eb58f4e6ed38563887032","tid":1984344,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"64792871fcd9fe7fcc7dfdec62e1563035a76bca","tid":1984344,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb1741c4c2eaadd42f71ec884068c22fc455271","tid":1984344,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"波蘭真係好珍惜自己文化，睇下witcher3賣成點就知將本土野推廣開去有幾大市場"},{"pid":"e79bde72cdf5da403254e7961644b04babd64203","tid":1984344,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"me too"},{"pid":"c1b7a6a431d5e72ed8506505fbd54e8ee81bcb58","tid":1984344,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d48987fe27e4aa6803adfea8b997b5c572acb143","tid":1984344,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"波蘭在 1795 年被奧地利、普魯士和沙俄瓜分，之後半個世紀經歷三個抗爭階段，先是民眾自發起義，然後承拿破崙崛起尋求法國援助，及最後自己武裝起來與佔領國軍事對抗，均告失敗。<br />\n<br />\n半世紀過去了，波蘭損失大量人力物力，無法撼動佔領國半分，人民仍活在佔領國極權壓迫之下。<br />\n<br />\n痛定思痛後，波蘭人改變自身的抗爭模式，是為實證主義思潮運動。<br />\n<br />\n不談哲學，我們實際看看波蘭版實證主義做些甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n一、發展能自給自足的本土經濟。一民族之經濟依賴外方必然弱勢，在佔領國面前更無議價能力。而且，鼓勵消費本土產物和服務帶動本土生產的模式，不同階層各有得著，可調和社會上必然產生的各種階層矛盾，在本土經濟振興民族的目標下凝聚所有階層，減少內耗。<br />\n<br />\n二、盡力在政商各行各業爭取領導和上層位置，盡力治學，盡力創作，讓波蘭人有改變社會所處的機會和能力，並以波蘭人的身分以科學和藝術貢獻世界，讓世界知道波蘭確切的存在。<br />\n<br />\n三、將民族認同定義於文化和思維層面，脫離傳統的種族、地域模式。之前以種族定義民族，佔人口不少且認自己為波蘭人的波蘭猶太人被排除在外，並受到不同程度的歧視和迫害，如此傷害了波蘭民族的元氣。以地域定義民族，地域是各方必爭之擁有實體，對於保衛實體的抗爭，容易局限和執著於武力方面，以致損兵折將。反之，建基於文化和思維的認同感較能包容不同種族、宗教、思想的人，較温和以包括社會中的不同光譜，也較能隨著社會進步而靈活變化和發展。<br />\n<br />\n這不只是求存的法門，更是提高全民質素的長遠工程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/極權求生錄-六-波蘭人武力抗爭失敗後的長期對抗模式/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E9%8C%84-%E5%85%AD-%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%2F&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=c1c3da42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E9%8C%84-%E5%85%AD-%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%2F&h=c2881178\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/極權求生錄-六-波蘭人武力抗爭失敗後的長期對抗模式/</a><br />\n<br />\n環境幾惡劣都總會有野做到<br />\n唔好習得性無助同絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yxW0rj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yxW0rj.png&h=5f17ce6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4af57cf556522be21450ba47c5aa08ff95ab9411","tid":1984344,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24a69e690199accf7ce4fb4c11c8fb1a352a8c0b","tid":1984344,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dfa872786e08d8eb5c0706cfa0e0886ba0ffef26","tid":1984344,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:40:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係外國<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:41:59.000Z","msg":"蘇聯比中國更難以憾動<br />\n美國立國咁多年只有蘇聯呢一個競爭對手威脅到佢<br />\n佢地都照抗命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"無嘢無可能,首要條件唔好自己打沉自己"},{"pid":"e3c91a93ea89637caab42154ceb059c7b0b2eace","tid":1984344,"uid":353228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:12:34.000Z","msg":"如今示威都有狗拉。"},{"pid":"7bfb28f8b31d97a8a8605b79cf4986fb9a8dc783","tid":1984344,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:18:31.000Z","msg":"一齊堅持"},{"pid":"2c15887373dab73e9579eb05d505d1e57cc43736","tid":1984344,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd5064b3ba3a780c0e4076d931ff933154d110d7","tid":1984344,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:23:40.000Z","msg":"呢個最壞情況就係目前情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac